text: Agostinho da Silva Araujo (born 28 August 1997),https://int.soccerway.com/players/agostinho-araujo-da-silva/373259/ also known as Agostinho, is a football player who currently plays for Timor-Leste national football team. ==International career== Agostinho made his senior international debut against Mongolia national football team in the 2018 FIFA World Cup qualification (AFC) on 12 March 2015.http://www.national-football- teams.com/matches/report/12663/East_Timor_Mongolia.htmlhttps://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/03/12/asia/wc- qualifying-asia/timor-leste/mongolia/2012938/?ICID=PL_MS_01 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:East Timorese footballers Category:Timor-Leste international footballers Category:F.C.
